, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kt-tunstall@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kt-tunstall">KT Tunstall</a>被任命为今年艾弗·诺韦洛杰出歌曲集奖的获得者。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beth-gibbons-lives-outgrown-portishead-3756535">贝丝·吉本斯 (Beth Gibbons) – 《Lives Outgrown》评论：Portishead 歌手的独奏弓是对时间和损失的迷人研究</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（5月16日），艾弗斯学院宣布Tunstall成为继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>等人之后<a href="https://ivorsacademy.com/news/kt-tunstall-to-receive-an-ivor-novello-award-for-outstanding-song-collection-with-prs-for-music/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第58位获奖者</a>。最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kamille">Kamille</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kamille-talks-her-ivor-novello-win-ai-music-and-working-with-nile-rodgers-3444308">荣获 2023 年这一享有盛誉的奖项</a>。</p><p> Tunstall 将于 5 月 23 日星期四在伦敦 Grosvenor House 举行的 The Ivors with Amazon Music 颁奖典礼上颁奖。颁奖典礼将于英国夏令时下午 4 点开始，可<a href="https://music.amazon.com/live/events/LZNE6VMB4G?tag=linkfiregen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;ascsubtag=a531169ab939e31caf565e92f5955131&amp;ref=dmm_acq_soc_sg_u_lfire_lp_x_a531169ab939e31caf565e92f5955131" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>进行直播。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7CToYMoRUN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="p